reckon with the threats of Qd5 and Qf3.} Bb7 $1 12. e6 {The move I like most.
Nevertheless, we should point out that White has a variety of promising
options in this position.} ({An interesting alternative is} 12. Nxb5 $5 {
If you prefer this move, you can definitely go deeper. Black will again have
to face huge practical problems.}) 12... Bxc3+ 13. bxc3 fxe6 14. Qc2 $36 {
White has terrific initiative for the sacrificed material. Even though the
computer might be able to hold this position as Black, in a practical game,
