the Gruenfeld with} 3... d5 $6 4. cxd5 Nxd5 {is dubious.} ({Maybe a better try
would be} 4... c5 $5 {Nevertheless, after} 5. dxc6 Nxc6 6. Nf3 Bg7 7. Nc3 O-O
8. e3 $14 {I doubt Black has enough compensation.}) 5. e4 Nb6 6. h5 $5 {
