typical position. Due to Black's spoiled coordination, instead of defending
the c3-pawn, White can play} 15. Nd2 Bxe2 16. Qxe2 Rxc3 $6 {This move is
dubious.} ({Better would have been} 16... b6 17. Rfc1 Qd7 18. c4 $14 {when
White enjoys only a slight advantage.}) {The point is that after} 17. Rfc1
