Nevertheless, I prefer the standard} 9. Nf3 ({After} 9. d6 axb5 10. Bxb5 Bb7
11. Nf3 Nc6 $5 ({But not} 11... Na6 {when after} 12. O-O Nb4 13. Qe2 Ne4 14.
