[%cal Gc1d2] Winning an important tempo and preparing Bd2 on the next move.}
Bc6 19. Bd2 $14 {White has an obvious advantage.}) 16. Qb5 Nxc3 ({Nothing gives
} 16... Rb8 17. Qd3 {when White keeps his extra material.}) 17. bxc3 Bc6 18.
